. 五年前的雨傘革命採用無了期佔領手法最終是失敗收場<br />\n2. 示威行動的參與人數必然隨時間的推進越嚟越少<br />\n3. 廣泛民議亦越來越不在示威者方，因為大部分港豬的想法就是袋住先<br />\n4. 想做任何行動， 要以不被補和不受傷的原則<br />\n<br />\n#必讀懶人包</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"8740ff56f1d52d3e058435fbc489ce7dbaa122a5","tid":1234682,"uid":9430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:29:34.000Z","msg":"開槍打頭點洗都洗唔甩"},{"pid":"ea01d58230505a2e40839d50bd09a5e98909767c","tid":1234682,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:29:40.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f5862a14ca8da009f2ed595b99eebd1826880e","tid":1234682,"uid":67272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:30:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17e9326d2474123ccb0cad0379087a41fb675f1a","tid":1234682,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:32:00.000Z","msg":"見一個屌人個<br />\n反人類罪"},{"pid":"cf643c96c0564d0adf6868f81af8a5f0f31f1713","tid":1234682,"uid":73621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a8dc9811427ddf359dcabc9235db6988c4439963","tid":1234682,"uid":111006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:24:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>洗佢老母</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/756665958097446?s=100001150726654&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F756665958097446%3Fs%3D100001150726654%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=4IeBTxJtadAFWj01jWWaWuSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=33fcfadc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/756665958097446?s=100001150726654&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/passiontimes/videos/1605772542888174?s=100001150726654&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpassiontimes%2Fvideos%2